class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="127"
data-flex-basis="305px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>剩下的都直接下一步即可。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://blog.molingran.com/p/home-assistant/onboarding2.webp"
width="2366"
